        "jsCode": "// Merge the 4 reference image binaries with the user image binary\nconst refItem = $('Combine Reference Binaries').first();\nconst userItem = $input.first();\n\nreturn [{\n  json: refItem.json,\n  binary: {\n    ...refItem.binary,\n    ...userItem.binary\n  }\n}];"
